{"tid":1775100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要做到全民勇武推翻政權？第一步，全民入維園。","createTime":"2019-12-08T15:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T06:26:30.000Z","uid":88420,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1ed87b0ce948a541c7592c86351edeb4c913f5","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"話說今日八十萬人大遊行，雖然天氣涼左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係好多手足，好多銀髮同細路都行得好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋一早入左維園，但係塞係裡面兩三個鐘，先出到圖書館。然後係聖保祿又停下行下，就算天氣涼左，都係好消耗體力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又，大家會問，遊行仲有無用？616、818，以至無不反對通知書嘅遊行，政府都唔理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，開始有人會期望，如果全民變勇武，咁就好啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要做到全民勇武，其實唔難。首先第一步，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民入維園</span></strong>。遊行嘅時候，全部人入維園，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好再中途加入</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n點解大家唔入維園？<br />\n<br />\n「嘩，要等好耐架啵」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「嘩，我入唔到啊」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「嘩，我約左個朋友，然後要等埋個姨媽姑爹」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔入維園，其實就係懲罰咁爲你付出嘅手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入維園嘅手足，就好似勇武咁，有老有嫩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好部分批評勇武手足，你對佢哋嘅貢獻視而不見，認為佢哋拖累社運，其實你係懲罰咁爲你付出嘅手足，荃灣健仔、岳巴、西灣河義士、陳彥琳、科大周梓樂，理大留守者，都係用生命為大家而奮鬥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔入維園，輕輕鬆鬆行完街，犧牲裡面嘅銀髮，裡面嘅小朋友，裡面堅持揹住小朋友嘅家長，大家對得住自己嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我地未必能夠為勇武擋子彈，但係我地可以入維園。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民入維園對遊行流速嘅好處，以至對於遊行隊伍機動性嘅提升，一早有好多分析。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n高士威道近天后、怡和街近渣甸坊崇光百貨係大路，加上遊行隊頭通常比較闊落，中途加入嘅人好容易就可以入隊。但係維園係細路出大路，如果大路已經迫滿中途加入嘅手足，係維園裡面嘅朋友就會好難入隊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">全民勇武，大家或者要有好多犧牲，亦都會因為唔同負擔，所以好難做到。咁不如，我地試下，下次遊行，全民入維園。</span><br />\n<br />\n只係會用多你一陣，但係大家都會快左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實入維園，並唔係咁困難。入維園，唔好做 free rider。所謂「和理非」，其實有好多種，大家一齊進步，好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所謂和勇不分，其實我估係大家能夠為對方著想，行多一步，而唔係單單其中一方去讓步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（side track，和理非呢個稱呼應該要改改。其實呢個 term 係由四方卿 propose 嘅「和理非非」演變出來，對於描述勇武以外嘅其他手足，個人認為唔夠準確性，和理非都有好多種的）</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再讓手足 suffer。要全民勇武嘅話：<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">第一步，全民入維園，好嗎？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔完美，可接受，但係需要改善改變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9ea2e5b97df32471a57795680817e43f22d576","tid":1775100,"uid":7342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42c883f0ed2a5aaf3683dbb39e480c0371709653","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b50092a956781dc299a7602f8854e44aaad633d","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"推多下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1369eefcf30c411ca28e0eb47dd794e3a393c01c","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"唔好再做自私鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行入維園，展現我地嘅秩序，以及追求民主嘅決心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d656bdc8b38ada3fd9629f168ffe3178a164c210","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aca4f15c46e2bf740847a73a5222fc5f4b2258","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"點解推唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362be97be18cb32269fdf210206702efe4cbe444","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"推 7/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6dddd99f1dcca66b7c83dd8c1f615cf2d36dbc","tid":1775100,"uid":305292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:45:55.000Z","msg":"係, 先入維園先到終點. 好似排隊咁."},{"pid":"5f7ab584dfc026bf992436c376a0223a49129cfd","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e6dddd99f1dcca66b7c83dd8c1f615cf2d36dbc","tid":1775100,"uid":305292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:45:55.000Z","msg":"係, 先入維園先到終點. 好似排隊咁."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"咁先係 fair<br />\n大家唔好再做自私鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家好多有心入維園嘅手足<br />\n見到次次都咁辛苦，就越來越無動力<br />\n<br />\n其實同唔少勇武手足嘅 frustration 一樣<br />\n付出左，有無用？<br />\n<br />\n入維園，等到自己出去，先到先走。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbbe69bac17cf3b42e0e92ab7e0822bd0b5ed8b","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"繼續推下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5300abc41247605d6810da89d868b715193b724a","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292cee0cdbdaf7b8a1c1ce26d7c95d082dec1bb0","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee67b400893fdfcfeef7213e8bcd110dcac9f970","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1290b27825e4650b84a61f317aee89daf7c40b","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2106313f0be16948836806aabb0ad6b5ddf065c8","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e772a4a5198466b0027e5113ae98bfa2458941a","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d210a715fec2c61accb73e1cd7f1c7fb153f1060","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ff4c32ca61c1264e1ae1b5810c46d6a7f78703","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b863eac5d12e21d5c3006b3dce105972d9885ff3","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61826f89ec82937dc829453b7f9b3342ac6de20","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T20:11:01.000Z","msg":"一月一見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c3cf5f48f91fc7323b236e9a20fae5183bfabd","tid":1775100,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T20:13:25.000Z","msg":"oush"},{"pid":"91052b2cba8723d4e1a3e3c94f93c13b44a8b750","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"希慎出面嘅人<br />\n如果你行得走得<br />\n麻煩入維園，好嗎？<br />\n裡面過百萬人就係因為你地貪快貪方便而 suffer<br />\n就過返去天后，去黃店食下嘢，等下，入維園，可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fe5108fc980f0d321408030c042242dd9450de","tid":1775100,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"2020 啦，大家齊齊進步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}